column5: Ive been away most of the summer, was wondering if I missed it.
I dont think its been announced yet
not me I was not in a sub way that I could enter the contest

C'mon guys it's ONLY been 7 weeks since the contest ended (August 14th).  We can't possibly expect things to take any less time than that.  From what happened last year - apparently the "legal issues" take a long time to sort through and that is apparently the reason for the LONG wait between the end of the contest and the announcement of the winner.
Yah, Dave's probably got them held up in court, trying to win his boat back
I think Daves on the right track better safe than sorry.   Art
im sure someone will win it who A) doesnt have a vehicle to tow it and B)doesnt fish.  lol
I have nearly a hundred entries... Glad to hear it hasn't been given away yet
Doesn't have a yoke on it Chad...  Michael
